#: projects/index.php:106
msgid ""
"Terminal is a modern terminal emulator featuring tabs and transparent "
"backgrounds."
msgstr ""
"Terminal adalah emulator terminal modern yang fiturkan tab dan latar "
"belakang lutsinar."

